  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK311">
<l>ciṟappīṉuñ celvam peṟiṉum piṟarkkiṉṉā</l>
<l>ceyyāmai mācaṟṟār kōḷ ceyyāmai mācaṟṟār kōḷ.</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is the determination of the spotless not to cause sorrow to others, although they could (by so causing) obtain the wealth which confers greatness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
